    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764970/extras/86ecd83bd5e9e71bfca7a86fb365a65e.avif?t=1726618264\" width=622 height=145 /></span><br>一款沉思的单人 2D 导航游戏，控制简单，但具有挑战性。<br><br>移动：A W S D 或 ← ↑ ↓ →<br>动作：空间<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>原创配乐和简洁的声音设计，营造身临其境的惊险体验。<br></li><li>游戏中有几个障碍，但“检查站”使体验的惩罚性降低。<br></li><li>在游戏过程中没有文本，也不需要它们。<br></li><li>动画、符号和机制向玩家传达了享受体验所需的一切。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764970/extras/49824b9ebfbd12467a46c504977e6eee.avif?t=1726618264\" width=622 height=272 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764970/extras/be99776b429f69f3ddcc405d8472ac46.webp?t=1726618264\" width=16 height=18 /></span> 一个黑暗而充满敌意的世界。这个地方有很多陷阱。<br>你能继续吗？你能找到吗？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764970/extras/26f56f65357d2171522b5b3038cbf9c5.webp?t=1726618264\" width=21 height=20 /></span>谨慎导航。慢慢来。注意线索。一切都会好起来的。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764970/extras/9638094d95d05e187f8e858ff66fca63.avif?t=1726618264\" width=622 height=95 /></span><br>以神秘的气氛，有时甚至是黑暗的，美丽的风景，“Echo - An Indie Tale”将征服你。",
